  "description": {
    "zh": "好久不见，还记得之前给你分配的那个用爆炸物干掉一些人的任务吗？这次我需要更具体的数据。你看，在塔科夫这里没有很多人拿着榴弹发射器跑来跑去，是时候改变这一点了。我会借你一个样品，好吗？你也会获得我们库存的使用权限。\n\n最近你的一些PMC“同事”一直在攻击我的猎犬，我不能让这事就这么算了，你知道吗？我要维持我的声誉，如果人们发现我让我的员工像猪一样在外面被屠杀……这么说吧，我损失很大，而你 however……无意冒犯，但这是事实。\n\n所以，你甚至知道怎么用这些东西吗？你终究得弄明白，不过我觉得我已经没有用户手册了，所以这事儿你得靠自己了，好吗？就帮我个忙，当你弄丢你的发射器时，别再来要另一个。",
    "en": "Long time no see, remember the task you were assigned to some time ago where you took down some guys with explosives? I need more specific data this time. You see, we don't have a lot of people running around with grenadelaunchers here in Tarkov, it's time to change that. I'll lend you a sample, alright? You will receive access to our stock aswell.\n\nLately some of your PMC \"colleagues\" have been attacking my hounds, I can't let that slide, you know? I got a reputation to maintain and if people find out that I let my employees get slaughtered out there like hogs... Let's just say I have a lot to lose, you however... No offense but that is the truth.\n\nSo, do you even know how to use these things? You'll have to find out eventually, I don't think I still have the user manuals though so you're kinda on your own here, alright? Just do me a favor, don't ask for another launcher when you lose yours."
  },
